.SH NAME
.PP
pc-logout - Clears locally stored API keys (managed and default), service account details (client ID and secret), and user login token. Also clears organization and project target context. This command is an alias for 'pc auth logout'.


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBpc logout [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Clears locally stored API keys (managed and default), service account details (client ID and secret), and user login token. Also clears organization and project target context. This command is an alias for 'pc auth logout'.


